                  </hi>. I am the prisoner's brother. The prosecutor sent down to me, to know if my brother had sold the cart, as he had bad it long enough to sell—I said I did not know.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430130-name-1035" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-1035" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
