                        <interp inst="t18430130-name-1035" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE CURRY</persName>
                  </hi>. About six weeks ago I met the prisoner in George-street—he said he was going to sell the cart and horse—he sold the horse, but could not sell the cart—he brought it back, and the prosecutor's son let him in at the gate.</p>
